configured right (if you have a joystick), or it\u0027s a trim issue. If you hold alt\u002B(w,a,s,d) it moves the zeroed position of that control, giving you a certain amount of trim. To fix that, hold alt\u002B(opposite direction) until the control indicator in the bottom left sits on the zero marker.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}